ActNational Energy Board Act
National Energy Board Act Part VI (Oil and Gas) Regulations
SubjectIssuance of Licence GL-333 - NewTimes Energy Ltd.
PrecisOrder approving the ISSUANCE OF LICENCE GL-333 to NewTimes Energy Ltd. to export natural gas, in the form of liquefied natural gas, from a point at the outlet of the loading arm of the natural gas liquefaction plant to be located in the vicinity of Prince Rupert, British Columbia.
